{"priority": "minor", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/58/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/58.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/58/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/58/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/issues/58/continous-joint-is-not-limited-to-0-2-pi"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/58/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Maurice Fallon", "uuid": "{8bca6a99-adab-444a-b7f0-81660c79adfb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B8bca6a99-adab-444a-b7f0-81660c79adfb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B8bca6a99-adab-444a-b7f0-81660c79adfb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/abb08cebf2b2b2fb3ae3f65fde4d36c0d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsMF-4.png"}}, "nickname": "mauricefallon", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:82a58458-5b27-457e-8e75-da6e16d4e3df"}, "title": "continous joint is not limited to [ 0 : 2*pi ]", "component": null, "votes": 0, "watches": 3, "content": {"raw": "I've added a continuously spinning joint with a laser - for the DRC robot's head to my own model:\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n#!c++\r\n\r\n  <joint name=\"head_hokuyo_joint\" type=\"continuous\">\r\n    <origin rpy=\"0 0 0\" xyz=\"0 0 0\"/>\r\n    <axis xyz=\"1 0 0\"/>\r\n    <parent link=\"head\"/>\r\n    <child link=\"head_hokuyo\"/>\r\n    <limit effort=\"5\" velocity=\"12\"/>\r\n    <safety_controller k_position=\"100.0\" k_velocity=\"100.0\" soft_lower_limit=\"-9.2146\" soft_upper_limit=\"10.7854\"/>\r\n    <dynamics damping=\"0.1\" friction=\"0\"/>\r\n  </joint>\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever when i query the angle when spinning clockwise:\r\n\r\n```\r\n#!c++\r\n\r\ndouble current_position = it->second->GetAngle(0).GetAsRadian();\r\n```\r\n\r\n... the angle is not limited to [ 0 : 2* pi].\r\nAnd after some time is a value in the 100s. There seems to be no wrap around here.\r\n\r\nThis is probably a bug in gazebo itself.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I've added a continuously spinning joint with a laser - for the DRC robot's head to my own model:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">joint</span> <span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;head_hokuyo_joint&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">type</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;continuous&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">origin</span> <span class=\"n\">rpy</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0 0 0&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">xyz</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0 0 0&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">axis</span> <span class=\"n\">xyz</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;1 0 0&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">parent</span> <span class=\"n\">link</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;head&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">child</span> <span class=\"n\">link</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;head_hokuyo&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">limit</span> <span class=\"n\">effort</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;5&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">velocity</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;12&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">safety_controller</span> <span class=\"n\">k_position</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;100.0&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">k_velocity</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;100.0&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">soft_lower_limit</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;-9.2146&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">soft_upper_limit</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;10.7854&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dynamics</span> <span class=\"n\">damping</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0.1&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">friction</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;0&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"n\">joint</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>However when i query the angle when spinning clockwise:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"kt\">double</span> <span class=\"n\">current_position</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">it</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">second</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">GetAngle</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">GetAsRadian</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>... the angle is not limited to [ 0 : 2* pi].\nAnd after some time is a value in the 100s. There seems to be no wrap around here.</p>\n<p>This is probably a bug in gazebo itself.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2012-12-10T17:25:12.385208+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2014-09-16T18:36:34.527898+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 58}